---
title: Hot Smoked Salmon Fishcake with Roasted Beetroot and Cucumber Pickle
description: Add a touch of luxury to your menu with delicious salmon fishcakes in a buttery prawn sauce. Light fluffy fishcakes made with flakes of hot-smoked salmon, fresh dill, chives, crème fraîche and mash coated in crunchy panko breadcrumbs and baked until crispy.
